                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-128-off618 t17850914-128-cd619"></join> last, four guineas, value 4 l. 4 s. four half-crown pieces, value 10 s. and six shillings in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850914-128-victim1285" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Hartley
