                  </persName>
             apprehended the prisoners, and found nothing upon them.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Mrs. Hutton was in liquor, she said she was very sorry for what she had done.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178509140171"></xptr>Prosecutor. The woman was quite sober before the magistrate.</p>
               <p>BOTH <rs id="t17850914-128-verdict621" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850914-128-verdict621" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
